* Martin Christopher as a wax model of Meriwether Lewis * Martin Sims as a wax model of William Clark * Randy Lee , Darryl Quon , Gerald Wong , and Paul Chih - Ping Cheng as wax models of the Huns * Brad Garrett as the voice of the Easter Island Head
* Crystal the Monkey as Dexter , a stuffed capuchin monkey PRODUCTION Section::::Production .
The building featured in the film , which was constructed on a sound stage in Burnaby , British Columbia , is based on the American Museum of Natural History in New York City , external shots of which were used in the movie .
Trainers spent several weeks training Crystal , who plays the troublemaking monkey Dexter , to slap and bite Stiller in the film .
Robin Williams ' Theodore Roosevelt costume closely resembles that of John Wayne 's character in The Shootist .
Director Shawn Levy credited Ben Stiller for the ensemble cast : " When actors hear that Ben Stiller is in a movie they want to work with him .
It [ 's ] a high - water mark
and it absolutely draws actors in
and I 'm convinced that 's a big part of why we got this cast . "
