Ref .
Kids ' Choice Awards MTV Movie Award National Movie Award Teen Choice Award Taurus Award Young Artist Award SEQUELS Section::::Sequels .
The first installment in the trilogy , Night at the Museum was followed by a sequel titled Night at the Museum : Battle of the Smithsonian , which was released on May 22 , 2009 in North America .
The third and final installment , Night at the Museum : Secret of the Tomb , was released on December 19 , 2014 in North America .
In 2016 , The Hollywood Reporter stated that the Alibaba Pictures Group intended to remake the film .
